commit.message:
Add package reassignment script, moved from herdfix and updated

The package reassignment script we were using historically lived
in the herdfix repository, since it was derived from the scripts used
to remove herds from metadata.xml.  Let's move it here where it makes
more sense.  While at it, let's clean it up a bit.

Signed-off-by: Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org>
